"The amount we are contributing is very little but it means a lot when every member contributes. We pay less during death than is expected for NHIF. When I die, I want to give my family easy time. I don't want to bother people. Many members aim at burying themselves," she said. The child's decomposing body was discovered without the head, hands and legs. Kenya Railways said that the new prices will remain in place for the next 90 days. Sonko defends himself on second day of impeachment sitting. Sonko accuses mover of the impeachment motion of dramatising the bursary issue to protect a powerful cartel of MCAs. Somalia’s President facing accusations of misusing foreign-trained police units to harass top presidential contenders.